## Battle End System -- Implementation Plan

### Overview

This plan covers 6 interconnected features: victory/defeat detection, battle loot system, battle result data expansion, resource persistence, battle result settlement UI, and defeat handling. The implementation follows the existing project patterns: BindWidget UI, delegate-driven communication, Chinese comments, and the LFP class prefix.

### Complete Data Flow

```
Unit dies → HandleDeath() → OnDeathDelegate broadcast
  → TurnManager::CheckBattleEnd() (new)
    → All enemies dead? → TurnGameMode::EndBattle(true)
    → All players dead? → TurnGameMode::EndBattle(false)
